# Package-local .gitignore.
# The repo-root .gitignore at ../../.gitignore covers the bulk of patterns
# (.env, .venv, __pycache__, *.db, *.log, .nexus*/, etc.). Keep this file
# minimal and only add patterns that are genuinely unique to this package.

# Real env (root already covers; duplicated as belt-and-braces).
.env

# Twin runtime caches when running standalone (root covers .nexus*/, but
# `.nexus/` bare needs an explicit entry — the root pattern is `.nexus_*/`
# with trailing underscore; here we cover the bare form too).
.nexus/
.nexus_*/

# Legacy "rune" runtime caches (pre-Phase G — wipe on sight).
.rune_twin/
.rune_*/
